3. Usage
B.R.O.K.E. provides dice rolling features, stores user macros (shortcuts for dice rolls), saves roll history, and allows for secret/private rolls.
By using the Bot, you agree not to abuse, spam, or use B.R.O.K.E. in any manner that violates Discord’s Terms of Service or community guidelines.

